name: What's your Story with Sarah Marcopolos

episodes.title: Escaping a cult environment to freedom, Tedx speaker Misty Gilbert.
episodes.description: What's your Story with Sarah Marcopolos Episode 2. Click and subscribe. Here we have special guest Misty GilbertTedx speaker and life coach. www.mistywgilbert.com She talks about her challenges of escaping a cult after sexual abuse to freedom. Her relationship with God and how she overcame to become an authentic businesswoman. Join us for her inspirational journey. And musical artist DJ Astronaut Derick Abram He will take you to the moon and back with music that is totally interstellar. https://soundcloud.com/thedjastronaut Don't forget to share and subscribe.
